Insert Logo, Title and resize. 11

Step 1: Insert Colaberry Logo


1-      Select Insert from the Ribbon

2-      Select Image

3-      Select the image from folder.

4-      Go to the General tab and adjust the size X- Position 0, Y-Position 0, Width 191, and Height 106

5-      Turn on the border and change the color to #E6E6E6.

Step 2: Insert the Title of the Dashboard


1-    Select Insert from the Ribbon

2-   Select Text box

3-   Write the Title Text type Segoe UI, Title Text Size 24, Year Text size 20, Bold and Center

4-   Go to the General tab and adjust the placement X- Position 191, Y-Position 0, Width 626, & Height 106

5-    Turn on the Border and change the color to #E6E6E6.

Step 3: Insert the US Department of Transportation Logo


1  Select Insert from the Ribbon

2  Select Image

 3-Select the image from folder.

4- Go to the General tab and adjust the size X- Position 817, Y-Position 0, Width 170, and Height 106

 5-Turn on the border and change the color to #E6E6E6.


To learn more on how to insert image, Logo and Text use the link below

https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/power-bi/create-reports/service-dashboard-add-widget
